                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240916-97-off529 t18240916-97-cd530"></join>, a pair of scales, value 1 s.; four brass weights, value 1 s.; a pair of shears, value 3 s.; a pint of tincture of rhubarb, value 8 s., and five bottles, value 5 d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18240916-97-victim851" type="victimName">
